body: This should be fixed by https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/commit/5c7f9e316d8c7735308a217310350d416d7498cc. Would you mind taking a look? If you also need the C API symbols for your custom ops, you can link against libtensorflow.so (although that will make the custom ops non-portable to other languages).
